ORLANDO, USA, August 4, 2019/APO Group/ -- 
                                                        
                            Twenty Youth from Seven African Countries to Represent Africa in the Second Jr. NBA Global Championship from Aug. 6-11 in Orlando, Florida.
        
                                    
                    
                        
                                                
                        
                        
